As I noted in [this other question][1], if your goal is specifically to return multiple values from a function, in Java 16+ you can accomplish something similar to this using a record type:

    record FooResult(int a, int b, int c) { }

    FooResult produceFoo() {
        return new FooResult(1, 2, 3);
    }

    /* ... */

